://static.codemao.cn/FnNA9Y9XtLGKtIHvM7AuhLGgdGsu\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;导入事先准备好的图片。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;点击那个“Aa”</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fut3prCZDH9cic98X1mJfvHmQvon\"><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;就这么简单。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;再用这张图弄上去，就OK了。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;好了下课。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;作业：创建一个小说，带上封面，截图给我，下方评论区。</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;下期再见。</p>","board_id":"2","board_name":"积木编程乐园","updated_at":1515224566,"created_at":1515221398,"n_views":55,"n_replies":3,"n_comments":0,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":false,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}